Join our ever growing Juka community.message: 加入我们不断增长的胡卡社区

We use \"Discord\" for managing the comm.message: We use "Discord" for managing the community as it provides an easy way to stay connected. In order to join the community, you should click and register a Discord account. If you already have an account, just join the "JukaLang" group. It's public and anyone can join!

Juka is built by the community, for the.message: Juka 是由社区为社区建造的。请考虑为Juka GitHub 仓库做出贡献

When you create new features, please fol.message: 当您创建新功能时，请遵循项目文档中指定的指南。

Juka is built on top of .NET framework..message: Juka是建立在.NET框架顶部的。 这意味着Juka可以在许多平台上运行，包括Windows、Linux、MacOS (即将来临)、iOS/iPadOS (即将来临)和Android。

You can run Juka on Microsoft's Azure Se.message: 您可以使用 Juka 内置的 Azure 功能在 Microsoft 的 Azure 服务器上运行 Juka 。

All packages are hosted on a blockchain.message: 所有软件包都以分散方式托管在区块链上。即将来临...
